title: Telerik 2015 Ultimate Pack
description:
Telerik Ultimate Pack 2015


Language: English


Included:


- Every single Telerik Product in 2014 Q1 - 2015 Q3 timeline.
- Source code, installers, DLLs, NuGet packages, documentation, samples, etc.


Made from sources from too many sites to list - many thanks to them!


Notes:

- EVERYTHING is LICENSED, no trials, no BS.
- Torrent is very divided/organized, so you can download only what you want.
- Only latest versions are included, so, for example, Telerik Reporting 2015 Q2 SP1 is included, but not older versions of Telerik Reporting are included.
- There are special cases where the source code is available only for an older version (respect to the newest installer), and the installer for the older version is also inlcuded in that case.
- Due to Telerik Data Access Visual Studio Designer not being available in post 2015 Q1 releases, an installer is provided for Telerik Data Access 2015 Q1.
- All products have the installers/binaries, but sources, help, samples, etc. won't always be there.
- Don't forget to get 7-Zip, many files are compressed with it to save space (otherwise it would be a 20+ GiB torrent).


Enjoy!
